<item>
            <title>[LU-19553] DKMS: add depends for additional packages lustre may depend upon</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19553</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When mlnx-ofed-kernel-dkms has been installed but not yet&lt;br/&gt;
built (new kernel has not yet booted) installing&lt;br/&gt;
lustre-client-dkms&lt;br/&gt;
fails to build correctly (due to building against an old set&lt;br/&gt;
of symbols).&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;This is theoretically true for several other possible&lt;br/&gt;
packages that lustre could be depending upon.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;mlnx-ofed-kernel&lt;br/&gt;
zfs&lt;br/&gt;
cray-kfabric (and its dependencies)&lt;br/&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;cray-cxi-driver, cray-slingshot-base-link, kdreg2, sl-driver&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
